{
  "id": "RAW_96f28385",
  "title": "苹果发布两款新 MacBook：AI 性能破纪录，最强显示器卖两万五",
  "url": "https://www.ifanr.com/1656640?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=",
  "date": "2026-03-03 23:35:04",
  "author": "马扶摇",
  "siteName": "爱范儿",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p>正如期待那样，苹果刚刚通过「官网直接上架」+「新闻稿」的方式，推出了最新的 M5 Pro/Max 款 MacBook Pro 和一大堆 Mac 更新。</p>\n  <p>这次上新的 MacBook Pro 相比昨天发布的「闹人」iPhone 17e，让人兴奋的元素少了一些。</p>\n  <p>毕竟它和爱范儿去年测试过的 M5 MacBook Pro 的唯一区别，就是处理器新增了 M5 Pro 和 M5 Max 两种规格，<strong>除此之外再无变化</strong>。</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1656641\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/1-MBP-BnW.jpeg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"5120\" height=\"3280\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/1-MBP-BnW.jpeg!720 5120w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/1-MBP-BnW-360x231.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/1-MBP-BnW-768x492.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/1-MBP-BnW-1024x656.jpeg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 5120px) 100vw, 5120px\"></p>\n  <p><span style=\"color: #999999;\">▲ 图｜Apple</span></p>\n  <p>而这次的 M5 Pro 与 M5 Max 处理器，的确有一些可以让人刮目相看的资质。</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1656642\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/2-M5-hero.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"1960\" height=\"1104\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/2-M5-hero.jpg!720 1960w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/2-M5-hero-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/2-M5-hero-768x433.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/2-M5-hero-1024x577.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1960px) 100vw, 1960px\"></p>\n  <p>M5 Pro/Max 相比标准版 M5，差异最大的自然是核心数量。</p>\n  <p>根据爱范儿去年基于标准版 M5 处理器的评测，哪怕仅仅 10+10 核心的 M5，在很多追求本地算力的应用中已经可以追平当年的「巨无霸」M1 Max 了。</p>\n  <p>而规模更大的 M5 Pro 与 M5 Max，毫无疑问将会成为 2026 年 Mac 家族中的性能标杆。</p>\n  <p>目前我们看到，M5 Pro 的起步配置为 15 核 CPU + 16 核 GPU，最高可选配 18 核 CPU + 20 核 GPU 的组合：</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1656643\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/3-m5-pro-spec.png!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"2444\" height=\"1036\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/3-m5-pro-spec.png!720 2444w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/3-m5-pro-spec-360x153.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/3-m5-pro-spec-768x326.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/3-m5-pro-spec-1024x434.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2444px) 100vw, 2444px\"></p>\n  <p>而 M5 Max 的核心配置则来到了 18 核 CPU + 32 核 GPU 起步、18 核 CPU + 40 核 GPU 封顶的规模。</p>\n  <p>鉴于本次 N3P 工艺的进步，双端性能再创新高不是梦：</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1656644\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/4-m5-max-spec.png!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"2466\" height=\"1234\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/4-m5-max-spec.png!720 2466w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/4-m5-max-spec-360x180.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/4-m5-max-spec-768x384.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/4-m5-max-spec-1024x512.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2466px) 100vw, 2466px\"></p>\n  <p>同时，本次 M5 家族的神经网络加速器规模同样不容小觑。</p>\n  <p>去年的标准版 M5 上，苹果就为每颗 GPU 核心都内置了「新一代神经网络加速器」，让 Msty Studio 和 VidHex 之类本地 AI 工具取得了不俗的效果：</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1656645\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/5-M5-vs-M1Max.png!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"1612\" height=\"902\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/5-M5-vs-M1Max.png!720 1612w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/5-M5-vs-M1Max-360x201.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/5-M5-vs-M1Max-768x430.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/5-M5-vs-M1Max-1024x573.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1612px) 100vw, 1612px\"></p>\n  <p><span style=\"color: #999999;\">▲ 在 Msty Studio 中使用相同指令测试首词元响应速度</span></p>\n  <p>而相同的神经网络加速器应用到 M5 Pro 与 M5 Max 规模更加庞大的 GPU 核心之后，其在本地机器学习和 AI 加速方面的表现只会更加出色——</p>\n  <p>根据苹果的介绍，M5 Pro 在 LLM 提示词中「相比 M1 Pro 可以实现 6.9 倍的提升」，M5 Max 则相比 M1 Max 实现了 6.6 倍的飞跃：</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1656646\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/6-compare.png!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"2026\" height=\"1530\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/6-compare.png!720 2026w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/6-compare-360x272.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/6-compare-768x580.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/6-compare-1024x773.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2026px) 100vw, 2026px\"></p>\n  <p>同时我们也能看到，在代码编译场景下，M5 Pro 不仅相比 M1 有接近 2.5 倍的提升，其表现甚至比 M4 Pro 都有了约 25% 的进步：</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1656647\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/7-compare.png!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"2044\" height=\"1540\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/7-compare.png!720 2044w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/7-compare-360x271.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/7-compare-768x579.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/7-compare-1024x772.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2044px) 100vw, 2044px\"></p>\n  <p>这种进步幅度可不是单纯堆砌 GPU 规模或者盲目提频能够实现的，台积电 N3P 工艺和改良过的架构设计在其中都功不可没。</p>\n  <p>同时，今年的 M5 Pro/Max 上还首次应用了一套「全新融合架构」，可以「将两颗芯片集成到单个 Soc 中」——</p>\n  <p>不出意料的话，这就是此前爆料中提到过的台积电 SoIC-MH 工艺，让不同架构的处理器单元可以更灵活地在晶片上排布。</p>\n  <h2>MacBook Air：提速！</h2>\n  <p>此外，本次处理器升级的不止 MacBook Pro，大半年没有更新的 MacBook Air 终于迎来了处理器升级。</p>\n  <p>按照计划，MacBook Air 从 M4 升级到了 M5，有 10+8 核与 10+10 核两种规模，依然为 16、24 和 32GB 三款内存：</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1656648\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/8-air-up.png!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"2372\" height=\"1180\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/8-air-up.png!720 2372w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/8-air-up-360x179.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/8-air-up-768x382.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/8-air-up-1024x509.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2372px) 100vw, 2372px\"></p>\n  <p>最重要的好消息在于，这一代 MacBook Air 的硬盘<strong>起步配置</strong>来到了 512GB，价格 8499 元起（13 寸）。</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1656649\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/9-air-disk.png!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"2440\" height=\"1682\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/9-air-disk.png!720 2440w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/9-air-disk-360x248.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/9-air-disk-768x529.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/9-air-disk-1024x706.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2440px) 100vw, 2440px\"></p>\n  <p>并且过去几年「硬盘掉速」的问题终于得到了苹果的重视，根据官网上的说法，新版 MacBook Air 换用了新的 SSD，读写速度提升了两倍。</p>\n  <h2>苹果显示器：影分身！</h2>\n  <p>整整五年没更新的 Studio Display 终于在这个春天得到了新生，并且还夺舍了自家大哥 Pro Display XDR——</p>\n  <p>是的，你没看错，<strong>Pro Display XDR 没有了</strong>，现在官网只剩下 Studio Display 和 Studio Display XDR：</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1656650\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/10-displays.png!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"2226\" height=\"1622\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/10-displays.png!720 2226w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/10-displays-360x262.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/10-displays-768x560.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/10-displays-1024x746.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2226px) 100vw, 2226px\"></p>\n  <p>与预测的相同，新款用上了之前 CES 上 LG 展示的那块高刷 5K 面板（或类似物），让 Studio Display XDR 解锁了 ProMotion 能力。</p>\n  <p>只不过等级森严的传统不能丢，虽然 Studio Display XDR 更新了 120Hz 刷新率，<strong>但新 Studio Display 依然是 60Hz。</strong></p>\n  <p>但 5K 120Hz 绝不是个轻松的参数，以至于苹果官网自己都要标明：</p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p>搭载 M1、M1 Pro、M1 Max、M1 Ultra、M2 和 M3 芯片的 Mac 机型搭配 Studio Display XDR 使用时，刷新率最高达 60Hz 。</p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1656651\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/11-xdrr.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"2520\" height=\"1360\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/11-xdrr.jpg!720 2520w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/11-xdrr-360x194.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/11-xdrr-768x414.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/11-xdrr-1024x553.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2520px) 100vw, 2520px\"></p>\n  <p>而在软件方面，Studio Display XDR 还带来了一样新东西：DICOM 医学影像校准。根据官网的介绍：</p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p>Apple 发布了全新的 DICOM 医学影像预设和医学影像校准器，使放射科医生能够直接在 Studio Display XDR 上查看诊断图像，为单一用途的医学影像显示器提供了一种多功能替代方案，并支持无缝显示模式切换。</p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p>还记得医院墙上那个用来看 CT 的背光板吗？现在 Studio Display XDR 可以借助自己 2000 尼特的峰值 HDR 亮度来给医生帮忙了：</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1656652\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/12-ct.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"1960\" height=\"1104\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/12-ct.jpg!720 1960w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/12-ct-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/12-ct-768x433.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/12-ct-1024x577.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1960px) 100vw, 1960px\"></p>\n  <p><strong>新版 Studio Display XDR 和 Studio Display 的起售价分别为 24,999 元和 11,999 元。</strong></p>\n  <h2>存储价格：还得涨！</h2>\n  <p>对于 2026 年那个逃不开的话题，新 Mac 产品家族的各项<strong>存储规格</strong>也值得大家更密切的关注。</p>\n  <p>以最具代表性的 MacBook Pro 来说，本次 M5 Pro/Max 处理器依然提供 24、36、48、64、128GB 共五种可选的内存规格。</p>\n  <p><strong>但与上代的 M4 Pro/Max 面临的问题一样，M5 Pro/Max 的内存依然是严重「叉着卖」的。</strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1656653\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/13-split-ram.png!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"2452\" height=\"2032\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/13-split-ram.png!720 2452w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/13-split-ram-360x298.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/13-split-ram-768x636.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/13-split-ram-1024x849.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2452px) 100vw, 2452px\"></p>\n  <p>换句话说，基础 15+16 核心的 M5 Pro 只有 24 和 48GB 两种规格可选。<strong>想要升级到 36GB 内存，就必须加 2000 元选择 18+20 核心的才行。</strong></p>\n  <p>为了让大家看得更直观，我们制作了这个对照表来帮大家理解：</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1656654\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/14-ram-table.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"1302\" height=\"720\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/14-ram-table.jpg!720 1302w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/14-ram-table-360x199.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/14-ram-table-768x425.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/14-ram-table-1024x566.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1302px) 100vw, 1302px\"></p>\n  <p>相比劈叉的统一内存，新 MacBook Pro 的硬盘反而单纯了许多，还是熟悉的 1TB、2TB、4TB、8TB 组合，以前的 512GB 选项被取消了：</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1656655\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/15-storage.png!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"2448\" height=\"1658\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/15-storage.png!720 2448w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/15-storage-360x244.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/15-storage-768x520.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/15-storage-1024x694.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2448px) 100vw, 2448px\"></p>\n  <p>苹果或许能够在体量相对比较小的 iPhone 17e 上「加量不加价」。但对于 512GB 起步、8TB 封顶的 MacBook Pro 来说，存储价格压力依然不容小觑。</p>\n  <p>比较好玩的是，目前苹果官网的预购页面上，仍然提供 Final Cut Pro 与 Logic Pro 的买断制选项。</p>\n  <p>在顶上，苹果只用一行不起眼的小字列出了 Apple Creator Studio 服务：</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1656656\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/16-Software-addon.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"3142\" height=\"1966\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/16-Software-addon.jpg!720 3142w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/16-Software-addon-360x225.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/16-Software-addon-768x481.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/16-Software-addon-1024x641.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 3142px) 100vw, 3142px\"></p>\n  <p><span style=\"color: #999999;\">▲ 图｜Apple</span></p>\n  <p>需要注意：根据苹果此前的说法，通过 ACS 订阅的那些工具软件（包括创意工具和 iWork 三件套）和此前买断的版本，后续在功能性和 AI 能力上会产生版本差异。</p>\n  <p><strong>如果你计划后面三五年都持续使用苹果创意全家桶的话，还是直接订阅 Apple Creator Studio 更省事一些。</strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1656657\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/17-ACS.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"1260\" height=\"680\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/17-ACS.jpg!720 1260w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/17-ACS-360x194.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/17-ACS-768x414.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/17-ACS-1024x553.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1260px) 100vw, 1260px\"></p>\n  <p><span style=\"color: #999999;\">▲ 图｜Apple</span></p>\n  <p>考虑到 M5 Pro 和 M5 Max 是眼下整条 Mac 线中「无可争议的性能之巅」，对于那些需要 MacBook Pro 出外勤去现场剪辑、临时编译、移动调色的「prosumer」来说，这个价格相比之前<strong>其实没什么大区别</strong>。</p>\n  <p>也应了爱范儿之前的选购建议：</p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p><strong>明确需求，该买就买，买新不买旧。</strong></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p>毕竟 MacBook Pro 作为一款工具属性拉满的产品，对于大多数人来说，<strong>如果你买它不是为了挣钱的话，那么大概率是没有必要买的。</strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1656658\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/18-mbp-16inch-on-the-go.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"1312\" height=\"738\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/18-mbp-16inch-on-the-go.jpg!720 1312w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/18-mbp-16inch-on-the-go-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/18-mbp-16inch-on-the-go-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/18-mbp-16inch-on-the-go-1024x576.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1312px) 100vw, 1312px\"></p>\n  <p><span style=\"color: #999999;\">▲ 图｜AppleInsider</span></p>\n  <p>同时记得关注爱范儿，我们将在后续为大家带来 M5 Pro/Max 款 MacBook Pro，以及本次苹果春季发布会上其他重点新品的完整评测。</p>\n </body>\n</html>",
